rows.label: qst000511_msg0001
rows.name: Norman... We should get going soon...

rows.label: qst000511_msg0002
rows.name:
Indeed...
Thank you for your help, friends.

rows.label: qst000511_msg0003
rows.name:
I cannot thank you properly,
here, like this...

rows.label: qst000511_msg0004
rows.name:
If you ever come to Superbia,
please come and see us.

rows.label: qst000511_msg0005
rows.name:
Yes! Then we'll be able to properly
repay your kindness!

rows.label: qst000511_msg0006
rows.name:
We'll never forget what you did for us.
I promise!

rows.label: qst000511_msg0007
rows.name: Thanks again. We're in your debt.
